name: MetAIverse
description: Open Source AI Metaverse -- Simplified 3D AI Agent Creation Effortlessly build and interact with 3D AI agents to shape the future of virtual worlds. The Future of 3D AI Agents. Our mission is to empower creators and innovators by making the creation and interaction with AI agents seamless and accessible.
